1)To build the container from the Dockderfile:--

      docker build -t sandeep/vnc .

2)To run the container sandeep/vnc:-

      sudo docker run -it --rm -p 5901:5901 sandeep/vnc

3)Connecting to the container from the vnc client:--

      Connect to vnc://<host>:5901 via your VNC client. currently the password is hardcoded to “acoman”
